<SUMMARY>
SUMMARY:

 This proposed rule would amend the regulations to set forth the acreage reduction percentage, if any, and the national
average price support rate for the 1995 crop of rice. This action is required by section 101B of the Agricultural Act
of 1949 (1949 Act), as amended. This proposed rule outlines a range of acreage reduction percentage options proposed
for the 1995 crop of rice and requests comments regarding price support rate adjustments for different types and grades
of rice.


</SUMMARY>
