The Enstrom Helicopter Corporation (Enstrom) issued Service Directive Bulletin (SDB) No. 0069, Revision A, dated
July 9, 1990, that contains an overhaul time interval for clutch assemblies, P/N 28-13401-2 (Formsprag
CL 40526-8) and P/N 28-13401-4 (Formsprag CL 40526-10). Also, AD 89-04-09 referenced
neither Enstrom Service Information Letter (SIL) No. 0084, dated December 19, 1978, pertaining to checking the run-out
