Act, 5 U.S.C. 701 

et seq.

, provides generally for judicial review of final agency action, which in certain circumstances may include this
proposed rule. The Administrative Procedure Act does not require submission of a petition for reconsideration or
other administrative proceedings before parties may file suit in court. 


